snippet.title: 3 Days to Kill Official Trailer #1 (2014)

3 Days to Kill Official Trailer #1 starring Amber Heard, Hailee Steinfeld, Kevin Costner and directed by McG

Trying to reconnect with his estranged daughter, a dying Secret Service Agent is offered an experimental drug that could save his life in exchange for one last assignment.
